Check test.sh for usage.

If you plan to use checkout-clone or checkout-update you'll need to patch git with patches/write-raw.

If you plan to use fast-import you would need to patch git with patches/fast-import.

== troubleshooting ==

If you get this error:
stack level too deep (SystemStackError)

run:
ulimit -s 102400

